---
layout: post
title: Custom options for intent chosoer 
tag: Android
---

In our day to day Android app development work. There are time to time scenario we have to provide action selection dialog for various purpose. Here is a alternative to custom a dialog, use a chooserIntent to create System provided selection dialog with custom selection.


Here goes the 
```kotlin
Intent.createChooser(baseIntent, title).apply {
    putExtra(Intent.EXTRA_INITIAL_INTENTS, extraIntentArrays)
}
```


